<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261713>
    dc:description "FIGURE 64. Coelophora bissellata Mulsant: a. adult, nominate form; b. adult, variant; c. head; d. antenna; e. maxilla; f. abdominal postcoxal line; g. coxite; h. spermatheca; i–l. male genitalia: i. tegmen, lateral view; j. tegmen, ventral view; k. penis; l. penis apex." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261713/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261717>
    dc:description "FIGURE 65. Coelophora bissellata Mulsant, life stages: a–k. larva; l–n. pupa; o–r. adult." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261717/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261719>
    dc:description "FIGURE 66. Coelophora bissellata Mulsant, adult, variants: a–d. fully spotted adult; e–h. adult with reduced spots." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261719/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8261706>
    dc:description "FIGURE 62. Coelophora bissellata Mulsant: a. head; b. antenna; c. abdominal postcoxal line; d. prosternal process and mesoventrite; e. coxite; f. spermatheca; g–i. male genitalia: g. tegmen, ventral view; h. tegmen, lateral view; i. penis." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8261706/files/figure.png" ;
